	<Title>
		Smoking: Does it cause wrinkles?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Smoking leads to premature skin aging &amp;mdash; and more wrinkles.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is it true that smoking causes wrinkles?
	</Question>
